Introduction

Eunseo is a member of the girl group Cosmic Girls/WJSN and she represents the Gemini sign in the groups concept. Seola, Dayoung, Exy, Eunseo, Cheng Xiao, Soobin, and Yeoreum are in YTeen which is the Starship unit with Monsta X. She's part of the sub-unit 'Joy'.

She debuted as a member of WJSN on February 25, 2016 with their first mini album Would You Like?

On May 12, 2021, she debuted as a member of WJSN's sub-unit, WJSN THE BLACK, with the single album "My Attitude".
